OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FThe Senegalese government has accused
OL,8,FAfrican football's governing body of
OL,9,F"corruption" after the country was
OL,10,Fstripped of its Africa Cup of Nations
OL,11,Fwin.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, the Confederation of
OL,14,FAfrican Football (CAF) took away
OL,15,FSenegal's crown and awarded it to
OL,16,FMorocco, overturning Senegal's 1-0
OL,17,Fwin. Instead, they imposed a 3-0
OL,18,Fdefeat.
OL,20,FThe match took place on January 18 in
OL,21,FRabat, Morocco.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
