FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773921770
OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FThe appeal board determined Senegal
OL,8,Fhad forfeited the match when they left
OL,9,Fthe field in protest at a disputed
OL,10,Fpenalty awarded to Morocco in stoppage
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FThe walk-off led to a lengthy delay,
OL,14,Fand when the game was belatedly
OL,15,Frestarted, Brahim Diaz saw his spot-
OL,16,Fkick saved by Edouard Mendy.
OL,18,FPape Gueye went on to score the
OL,19,Fwinning goal for Senegal in extra time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
