PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773921770
OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FITV News has contacted the CAF for
OL,8,Fcomment.
OL,10,FSenegal's football federation has
OL,11,Falready indicated it intends to appeal
OL,12,Fagainst the decision to the Court of
OL,13,FArbitration for Sport (CAS).
OL,15,FIt said in a post on X: "(Senegal)
OL,16,Frequests the opening of an independent
OL,17,Finternational investigation into
OL,18,Fsuspicions of corruption within the
OL,19,FCAF's governing bodies."
OL,26,@wD@YOU{D@XO]
