OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773921770
OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FThe post described the decision to
OL,8,Foverturn the original result as
OL,9,F"unprecedented" and added: "It
OL,10,Fproceeds from a manifestly incorrect
OL,11,Freading of the rules, leading to a
OL,12,Fgrossly illegal and profoundly unjust
OL,13,Fdecision."
