PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773921770
OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FThe Moroccan federation is expected to
OL,8,Fmake a further statement on Wednesday,
OL,9,Fhaving said on Tuesday night: "The
OL,10,Ffederation wishes to recall that its
OL,11,Fapproach has never been intended to
OL,12,Fchallenge the sporting performance of
OL,13,Fthe teams participating in this
OL,14,Fcompetition, but solely to request the
OL,15,Fapplication of the competition's
OL,16,Fregulations."
OL,26,@qD@_OUxD@MO]
