PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773921770
OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FEverton's Idrissa Gueye, part of
OL,8,FSenegal's victorious squad, posted in
OL,9,Fan Instagram story: "Titles, trophies,
OL,10,Fmedals... all of this is fleeting.
OL,11,FWhat really counts is that each
OL,12,Fsupporter can go home and be reunited
OL,13,Fwith their family.
OL,15,F"The Senegalese people have shown what
OL,16,Fthey are: dignified in victory,
OL,17,Fdignified in adversity. We know what
OL,18,Fwe experienced that evening in Rabat.
OL,19,FAnd that, no-one can take away from
OL,20,Fus."
OL,26,@qD@UOUwD@AOU|D@DO]
