OL,3,CSenegal government accuses CAF of
OL,4,C'corruption' after AFCON triumph
OL,5,Coverturned
OL,7,FBoth betting companies, Paddy Power
OL,8,Fand BOYLE Sports have said they would
OL,9,Fpay out to customers who had backed
OL,10,FMorocco to win the match.
